# Segment Settings
msgctxt "#31000"
msgid "Segment Keywords to Watch For"
msgstr "Segmentnøgleord at overvåge"

msgctxt "#31001"
msgid "Skip Behavior Preferences"
msgstr "Spring over-adfærd"

msgctxt "#31002"
msgid "Always Skip These"
msgstr "Spring altid over disse"

msgctxt "#31003"
msgid "Ask to Skip These"
msgstr "Spørg om at springe over disse"

msgctxt "#31004"
msgid "Never Skip These"
msgstr "Spring aldrig over disse"

msgctxt "#31005"
msgid "Ignore unmapped EDL actions"
msgstr "Ignorer ikke-kortlagte EDL-handlinger"

msgctxt "#31006"
msgid "EDL Action Type Mapping"
msgstr "EDL-handlingstypekortlægning"

msgctxt "#31007"
msgid "Ignore overlapping segments"
msgstr "Ignorer overlappende segmenter"

msgctxt "#31011"
msgid "Open Segment Editor when overlaps are detected"
msgstr "Åbn segmentredigering når overlappende opdages"

msgctxt "#31012"
msgid "After parsing your sidecar, if overlapping or nested segments are still present while “Ignore overlapping segments” is off, open the Segment Editor once per playback file so you can fix the list. Requires Segment Editor to be enabled. Uses the same detection as the overlapping-segments notification."
msgstr "Efter parsing af din sidecar-fil, hvis overlappende eller indlejrede segmenter stadig er til stede, mens "Ignorer overlappende segmenter" er slået fra, åbnes segmentredigeringen én gang pr. afspilningsfil, så du kan rette listen. Kræver at segmentredigeringen er aktiveret. Bruger samme detektion som påmindelsen om overlappende segmenter."

msgctxt "#31008"
msgid "Use embedded chapters as fallback"
msgstr "Brug indlejrede kapitler som backup"

msgctxt "#31009"
msgid "When no sidecar (chapters.xml / .edl) or online segments are found, parse chapters embedded in the video file (MKV, MP4). Only chapters matching your custom segment keywords are used."
msgstr "Når ingen sidecar-fil (chapters.xml / .edl) eller onlinesegmenter findes, parse kapitler indlejret i videofilen (MKV, MP4). Kun kapitler der matcher dine tilpassede segmentnøgleord bruges."

msgctxt "#31010"
msgid "Segment Keywords"
msgstr "Segmentnøgleord"

msgctxt "#31013"
msgid "Prefetch next episode"
msgstr "Forudhent næste afsnit"

msgctxt "#31014"
msgid "When TV segment priority is Online first and TV online lookup is on, Skippy resolves the next library episode (same show: next episode in season, or first episode of the next season) and downloads merged online intro/recap segments in the background. Segments apply only when you start that exact file (path + ids must match). Verbose logging (All detail) logs prefetch schedule, store, and handoff. Not used for Local first. Never prefetches local sidecars."
msgstr "Når TV-segmentprioritet er Online først og TV-onlineopslag er aktiveret, løser Skippy det næste biblioteksafsnit (samme serie: næste afsnit i sæsonen, eller første afsnit i næste sæson) og downloader flettede intro/resumé-segmenter i baggrunden. Segmenter gælder kun, når du starter præcis den fil (sti + ID skal matche). Detaljeret logning (Alle detaljer) logger forudhentnings-tidsplan, opbevaring og overdragelse. Bruges ikke til Lokal først. Forudhenter aldrig lokale sidecar-filer."

# Dialog Settings
msgctxt "#32000"
msgid "Button Focus Style"
msgstr "Knap fokusstil"

msgctxt "#32001"
